import { createRouter, createWebHistory } from 'vue-router'
import DoctorDashboard from '../components/DoctorDashboard.vue'
import DoctorProfile from '../components/DoctorProfile.vue'
import OnlineConsultation from '../components/OnlineConsultation.vue'
import ArticlePublish from '../components/ArticlePublish.vue'
import CommunityForum from '../components/CommunityForum.vue'
import DoctorRanking from '../components/DoctorRanking.vue'

const routes = [
  { path: '/', component: DoctorDashboard },
  { path: '/profile', component: DoctorProfile },
  { path: '/consultation', component: OnlineConsultation },
  { path: '/publish-article', component: ArticlePublish },
  { path: '/community', component: CommunityForum },
  { path: '/ranking', component: DoctorRanking },
]

const router = createRouter({
  history: createWebHistory(),
  routes,
})

export default router
